{"tid":2285462,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政協經濟委員會副主任苗圩：中國人口老化愈趨嚴重　全面二胎未引發生育高峰","createTime":"2020-11-14T06:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T08:54:30.000Z","uid":39464,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"6bbc69d975f9a71295113dd51bca9f76beec44fc","tid":2285462,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T06:22:59.000Z","msg":"全國政協經濟委員會副主任、工業和信息化部前部長苗圩，今日（14日）在第11屆「財新峰會」上表示，近年以來，中國已經走出老人和兒童人口較少、勞動人口較多的「人口紅利期」，人口老化問題日趨嚴重，帶來的經濟增長、就業等一系列問題值得高度重視。苗圩指出，去年中國新生嬰兒有1465萬人，出生率降至10.48&permil;，預計2030年新增人口將進一步減至不足1100萬人。他強調，全面開放生育二胎後，沒有引發生育高峰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20201114/s00004/1605330475405/%e6%94%bf%e5%8d%94%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f%e5%a7%94%e5%93%a1%e6%9c%83%e5%89%af%e4%b8%bb%e4%bb%bb%e8%8b%97%e5%9c%a9-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e4%ba%ba%e5%8f%a3%e8%80%81%e5%8c%96%e6%84%88%e8%b6%a8%e5%9a%b4%e9%87%8d-%e5%85%a8%e9%9d%a2%e4%ba%8c%e8%83%8e%e6%9c%aa%e5%bc%95%e7%99%bc%e7%94%9f%e8%82%b2%e9%ab%98%e5%b3%b0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20201114%2Fs00004%2F1605330475405%2F%25e6%2594%25bf%25e5%258d%2594%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%25e5%25a7%2594%25e5%2593%25a1%25e6%259c%2583%25e5%2589%25af%25e4%25b8%25bb%25e4%25bb%25bb%25e8%258b%2597%25e5%259c%25a9-%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%258f%25a3%25e8%2580%2581%25e5%258c%2596%25e6%2584%2588%25e8%25b6%25a8%25e5%259a%25b4%25e9%2587%258d-%25e5%2585%25a8%25e9%259d%25a2%25e4%25ba%258c%25e8%2583%258e%25e6%259c%25aa%25e5%25bc%2595%25e7%2599%25bc%25e7%2594%259f%25e8%2582%25b2%25e9%25ab%2598%25e5%25b3%25b0&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNyxSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=18f95d73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20201114%2Fs00004%2F1605330475405%2F%25e6%2594%25bf%25e5%258d%2594%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%25e5%25a7%2594%25e5%2593%25a1%25e6%259c%2583%25e5